<p><a name="Non-fiction_2" id="Non-fiction_2"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Michael_Crichton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Non-fiction">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Non-fiction</span></h3>
<table class="wikitable">
<tr>
<th>Year</th>
<th>Title</th>
<th>Notes</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>1970</td>
<td><i><a href="/wiki/Five_Patients" title="Five Patients">Five Patients</a></i></td>
</tr>
