ael_Gallant" title="Michael Gallant">Michael Gallant</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Greg_Pratt" title="Greg Pratt">Greg Pratt</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Neela_Rasgotra" title="Neela Rasgotra">Neela Rasgotra</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Samantha_Taggart" title="Samantha Taggart">Samantha Taggart</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ray_Barnett" title="Ray Barnett">Ray Barnett</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Archie_Morris" title="Archie Morris">Archie Morris</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tony_Gates" title="Tony Gates">Tony Gates</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Simon_Brenner" title="Simon Brenner">Simon Brenner</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Catherine_Banfield" title="Catherine Banfield">Catherine Banfield</a></div>
